          "type": "data",
          "data": {
            "text/markdown": "<span class=\"markdown prose dark:prose-invert contents\"><h2 id=\"key-insights\">Key Insights</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>Bangladesh rose from 14% electricity access in 1991 to 99.5% by 2023</li>\n<li>Bhutan reached universal access (100%) by 2018, driven by hydropower development</li>\n<li>Cambodia went from under 20% in the late 1990s to 95% by 2023</li>\n<li>Ethiopia has more than quadrupled coverage to 55% but is still climbing</li>\n</ul></span>"
          }
        }
      ],
